---
---
<section id="hero" style="padding-top: 160px; border-bottom: none;">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow reveal">Argus — Nous × NVIDIA × Stripe Hackathon 2026</span>
    <h1 class="reveal" style="margin-top: 24px; max-width: 14ch;">
      The economic OS for an <span class="gpu">AI factory</span>.
    </h1>
    <p class="reveal" style="margin-top: 24px; max-width: 60ch; font-size: 18px;">
      Every autonomous agent burns two capitals: <span class="cash">cash</span> through Stripe
      and <span class="gpu">compute</span> through NVIDIA. Argus meters both into a single
      ledger, and allocates them toward margin — in real time.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-grid reveal" style="margin-top: 64px;">
      <div class="hero-tile">
        <span class="eyebrow cash">Cash</span>
        <p class="mono" style="margin-top: 12px; color: var(--fg); font-size: 28px;">$ 200.00</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 4px;">Job A revenue</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-tile">
        <span class="eyebrow gpu">Compute</span>
        <p class="mono" style="margin-top: 12px; color: var(--fg); font-size: 28px;">$ 15.32</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 4px;">Nemotron 3 Ultra burn</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-tile">
        <span class="eyebrow">Margin</span>
        <p class="mono" style="margin-top: 12px; color: var(--accent-2); font-size: 28px;">+ $ 184.68</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 4px;">Net, live</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .hero-tile {
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--bg-elev);
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
